    2539 SELGDISP ROM Superelement large displacements Main Index 4.If OPTION=1 the module expects the total displacements of the G-set in UX a.If only REFGRID1 is provided, the module will calculate the displacements of the G-set relative to rigid-body displacements based on the motion of REFGRID1. REFDISPO will be the displacements of the three REFGRID’s.

    2541 SEMA Assembles square symmetric matrices from upstream superelements Main Index Remark: XJJ may be purged. Example: Assemble stiffness matrix KGG and exit if there are missing upstream stiffness matrices. DBVIEW KAAUP = KAA WHERE (SEID=* AND PEID=* and WILDCARD) $ DBVIEW MAPUP = MAPS WHERE (SEID=* AND PEID=*) $ SEMA BGPDTS,SLIST,SEMAP,KJJ,KAAUP,MAPUP / KGG/ SEID/LUSETS/‘SEID’/-1 $ IF ( NOGO=-1 ) EXIT $
